subject: Australian Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Andy Roddick, nursing a shoulder injury, fell in five sets to Marin Cilic, and Andy Murray advanced when Rafael Nadal withdrew with a knee injury. On the women’s side, Justine Henin marched to the semis.
